<div class="title">A Bitter Bliss</div>
<div class="substance">Ayahuasca & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=kristybonay&Exact=1">kristybonay</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; kristybonay. "A Bitter Bliss: An Experience with Ayahuasca & Cannabis (exp45408)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 21, 2005. erowid.org/exp/45408</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
